"Interpolated values use a quadratic curve, and ease-in and ease-out. Icon: :"
"guilabel:`Circle`."
msgstr ""
"Milligildin nota ferningsferil og mjúka byrjun og endi. Tákn: :guilabel:"
"`Hringur`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "Línulegt"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid ""
"Interpolated values are calculated linear (each step value is equal). Icon: :"
"guilabel:`Diamond`."
msgstr ""
"Milligildin eru reiknuð línulega (hvert skref jafnt). Tákn: :guilabel:"
"`Tígull`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid "Constant"
msgstr "Fast"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Interpolated values stay the same until the next key frame, and jump to the "
"new value. Icon: :guilabel:`Square`."
msgstr ""
"Milligildin haldast óbreytt þar til næsti lykilrammi og hoppa svo í nýja "
"gildið. Tákn: :guilabel:`Ferningur`."

