msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "Rammahraði"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:134
msgid ""
"Adjust the frame rate of the animation. Typically, hand-drawn animations use "
"12 frames per second."
msgstr ""
"Stilltu rammahraða hreyfimyndarinnar. Venjulega nota handteiknaðar "
"hreyfimyndir 12 ramma á sekúndu."
